Seether - Seether: 2002-2013 [2013] [Anthology]
Wind-up / CD
MP3 / V0 (VBR) / C4

Seether 2002-2013 is a 2-disc compilation album by the South African rock band, Seether.
The first disc will comprise of the band's well-known songs and singles, while the second disc will comprise of a cover of Veruca Salt's song Seether, the name of which the band is named after, 2 new studio tracks, along with unreleased demos, B-sides, and soundtrack songs.
